{"tid":223700,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"青政清算科大編委","createTime":"2017-04-30T13:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T11:35:13.000Z","uid":113215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92414b86fffe781ccb734cf1f92a0fb9aeb88410","tid":223700,"uid":113215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:41:52.000Z","msg":"刊物涉嫌報導失實之聲明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本會日前收到一來自自稱為青年新政的支持者和選民的傳真，內容指本會出版之學生會官方刊物《振翅二十四．二》和《振翅二十四．三》中，部份文章「報導失實」，要求本會於科大的民主牆上公開道歉，並收回有關文章。惟對方未有留下任何聯絡方法，致本會未能作出跟進。<br />\n本會一直捍衛言論自由，鼓勵各方暢抒己見，更堅持編採自主，不接受任何外部人士干預。若文章內容確有誹謗或不實之處，煩請該傳真的作者主動聯絡本會，予以指教，本會亦願意致歉。但如有人以誹謗為名，打壓異己為實，此誠非本會及任何公民所能容忍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/s960x960/18192427_1258736647576679_6042994721844511908_o.png?oh=a2d98792aeb60dc763b540ad87ecd69b&amp;oe=599021C1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2Fs960x960%2F18192427_1258736647576679_6042994721844511908_o.png%3Foh%3Da2d98792aeb60dc763b540ad87ecd69b%26oe%3D599021C1&h=9f385891&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe5af59e0b663d2c89c2e61fb0282d1e95db48e4","tid":223700,"uid":14716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5893ad258b25549808f511289cbbd55b61aee1d6","tid":223700,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"呢啲信鳩寫都得啦"},{"pid":"2c38c622e572f113f91b04447f93e856cecb57f7","tid":223700,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"封信都唔係青政LETTERHEAD出<br />\n<br />\n屈人都屈好D啦"},{"pid":"969674f341dcbb248967481b8ee0f9166720f601","tid":223700,"uid":113215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>封信都唔係青政LETTERHEAD出<br />\n<br />\n屈人都屈好D啦</blockquote><br />\n都唔知邊撚個整封咁既信"},{"pid":"af842276c55b610f75850076d129b42a3cab85c9"